# <type>: <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>

# Type should be one of the following:
# * feat (new feature)
# * fix (bug fix)
# * docs (documentation)
# * style (formatting, missing semi colons, etc; no code change)
# * refactor (refactoring production code)
# * test (adding tests, refactoring test; no production code change)
# * chore (updating build tasks, package manager configs, etc; no production code change)
#
# Subject should use imperative mood and not end with period
# No more than 50 characters
#
# Body should explain what and why vs. how
# Can use multiple lines with "-" for bullet points
# Wrap at 72 characters
#
# Footer can contain issue references like "Fixes #123" or "Closes #123"